</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/utotenkopftz.showPublicProfile?language=EN>TotenkopfTZ</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(11/13/01 12:12:33 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm20.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=202.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.tallondirectorate.com/Toten1.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Kiting and Exping Galore</span><hr size=1> Splitpaw Gnolls would be good at 31. Heck, I think you can still get exp on them in 35. <p><br><center><font size = 4><font color=yellow><b>"Aces high, Baby...and you just drew the Death Card!"<b></font><br><center><font size = 2><font color=red><b>"A slap is just a hug that stings."<b></font><br><EMBED src="http://www.tallondirectorate.com/Toten9.swf" quality=high loop=true WIDTH=400 HEIGHT=100 TYPE="application/x-shockwave-flash" PLUGINSPAGE="http://www.macromedia.com/shockwave/download/index.cgi?P1_Prod_Version=ShockwaveFlash"> </EMBED></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ucaelestor.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Caelestor</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(11/13/01 2:48:56 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm20.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=202.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Kiting and Exping Galore</span><hr size=1> What you probably are forgetting is that you probably wouldnt get exp as fast quadding at low 30s, as you would<br>
