 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uaniar.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Aniar</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.docsmooth.com/images/dot.jpg" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Evoker</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(11/15/01 8:50:03 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm20.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=202.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.docsmooth.com/images/me.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Kiting and Exping Galore</span><hr size=1> Faster XP in a group in OT?  not even close.  1 blue per kite at lvl 30 is what I got.  That's 1 yellow / hour near guaranteed.  and no time spend finding a group.  the best I got in ANY group at lvl 30 was in Paw - 1 blue in 25 minutes.  I woulda gotten 2x that quadding.<br>
<br>
I hate quadding, but it works well.<br>
<br>
For gnolls in SK - the XP is great, but finding 4 of 'em sucks, due to overcamping. <p><br>Aniar Orrenson
